# ğŸ”  Typography

## Font Family

- Primary Font: Inter (Sans-serif)  
- Fallback: System UI, -apple-system, sans-serif  

## Font Sizes

- Heading 1: 2.25rem (36px)  
- Heading 2: 1.875rem (30px)  
- Heading 3: 1.5rem (24px)  
- Heading 4: 1.25rem (20px)  
- Body: 1rem (16px)  
- Small: 0.875rem (14px)  
- Extra Small: 0.75rem (12px)  

## Font Weights

- Regular: 400  
- Medium: 500  
- Semibold: 600  
- Bold: 700  

